---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="$BOUNCE - The Best Solana Memecoin">
	<main>
		<header>
			<div class="bouncing">
				<h1>$B<span class="o1">O</span><span class="o2">U</span>NCE</h1>
			</div>
			<p class="tagline">THE BOUNCIEST MEMECOIN ON SOLANA</p>
		</header>

		<section class="about">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>WHAT IS <span class="emphasis">$BOUNCE</span>?</h2>
				<div class="description">
					<p>$BOUNCE is not just another memecoin - it's an experience. Inspired by the glorious bounce of the markets and... well, other things that bounce wonderfully.</p>
					<p>Our philosophy is simple: <span class="emphasis">Everything that goes up must come down... and then UP AGAIN!</span></p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="image-container bouncing">
					<img src="/bouncy-gif-1.gif" alt="Bouncy animation" class="bouncy-image">
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="benefits">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>WHY CH<span class="o1">OO</span>SE $BOUNCE?</h2>
				
				<div class="benefits-grid">
					<div class="benefit-card pulsing">
						<h3>PERFECT PAIR</h3>
						<p>Two is always better than one. Our twin-token economy ensures maximum satisfaction!</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="benefit-card pulsing">
						<h3>FIRM SUPPORT</h3>
						<p>Our supportive community knows how to HODL properly. No sagging charts here!</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="benefit-card pulsing">
						<h3>AMAZING GROWTH</h3>
						<p>Watch your $BOUNCE grow to unimaginable proportions! Size matters in crypto.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="benefit-card pulsing">
						<h3>EXPLOSIVE POTENTIAL</h3>
						<p>Ready to experience financial climax? $BOUNCE knows how to finish strong!</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="image-container">
					<img src="/bouncy-gif-2.gif" alt="Another bouncy animation" class="bouncy-image">
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="quotes">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>WHAT PEOPLE ARE SAYING</h2>
				
				<div class="quote-container">
					<div class="quote">
						"I couldn't stop watching my $BOUNCE grow. The rise was... satisfying." <br>- Anonymous Trader
					</div>
					
					<div class="quote">
						"The twin-token system of $BOUNCE is the perfect pair. I love handling both at once!" <br>- Crypto Chad
					</div>
					
					<div class="quote">
						"$BOUNCE showed me that it's not about the size of your wallet, but how you use it." <br>- Diamond Hands Dave
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="image-container vibrating">
					<img src="/bouncy-gif-3.gif" alt="Excited bouncy animation" class="bouncy-image">
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="cta">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>READY TO EXPERIENCE THE B<span class="o1">O</span><span class="o2">U</span>NCE?</h2>
				<p class="emphasis">Grab $BOUNCE with both hands now!</p>
				
				<div class="buttons">
					<a href="#" class="btn bouncing">BUY $BOUNCE</a>
					<a href="#" class="btn pulsing">JOIN COMMUNITY</a>
				</div>
				
				<div class="disclaimer">
					<p>$BOUNCE is a meme token with no intrinsic value or financial promises. It's all about the bounce, baby!</p>
					<p>Not financial advice. DYOR. And remember - the harder the dip, the bigger the bounce!</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		width: 100%;
		overflow-x: hidden;
	}
	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1.5rem;
	}
	header {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 6rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		margin: 0;
		text-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
		letter-spacing: 2px;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}
	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
	}
	.emphasis {
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: yellow;
	}
	section {
		padding: 4rem 0;
	}
	.about {
		background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}
	.description {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.benefits-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin: 3rem 0;
	}
	.benefit-card {
		background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 10px;
		backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}
	.benefit-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-10px);
	}
	.quotes {
		background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
	}
	.quote-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}
	.quote {
		background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 10px;
		font-style: italic;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}
	.cta {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}
	.buttons {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2.5rem 0;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff1493, #ff69b4);
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 50px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}
	.btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
	}
	.disclaimer {
		margin-top: 4rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		opacity: 0.7;
	}
	.image-container {
		margin: 3rem auto;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		max-width: 600px;
		border-radius: 10px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.bouncy-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
	}
	.placeholder-text {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
		font-weight: bold;
	}
	.o1, .o2 {
		display: inline-block;
	}
	.o1 {
		animation: bounce 1.5s infinite;
		animation-delay: 0.2s;
	}
	.o2 {
		animation: bounce 1.5s infinite;
		animation-delay: 0.4s;
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: 3.5rem;
		}
		h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.tagline {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
		}
		.image-container {
			max-width: 100%;
		}
		.buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}
	}
</style>
